body.name: wirarpa Women's Underwear High Waisted Ladies Cotton Panties Soft Full Coverage Briefs 5 Pack (Regular & Plus Size)
features: Care instructions Hand Wash or Machine wash in cold with like colors. Non-chlorine bleach. Tumble dry low. We recommend hang drying for better and longer performance.

WIDE FABRIC COVERED WAISTBAND: Soft stretchy double-layer fabric covered waistband sits right at the waist. No rolling down or pinching. Our women's underwear is high rise, offers light tummy support with nice soothing feeling and reduces the appearance of muffin top.

STAY IN PLACE BRIEFS: Comfy ladies cotton underwear, suitable for postpartum c-section/ abdominal surgery recovery, after giving birth and those who have lower back problems. Aslo perfect for dresses/ high waisted jeans with no lines show through clothing.

FULL COVERAGE PANTIES: The Full coverage briefs with stretchy enough to make you feel secure. Easy on and easy off, not sexy but just comfortable. Nice alternative to "granny panty" type briefs. Wash well with less shrink.

DOUBLE-LAYER CROTCH: No ride up panties with double-layer crotch offer added protection. Chafe-free leg openings and high-waist full-coverage design avoid embarrassing adjustment all day time. Suitable for home, bedtime and everyday use.
We always expect your inquiry and support. Please let us know if there's any question. Your suggestion will help us to improve products and provide more great products.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are very nice! If you see the videos on the website, the white ones don't show that they are thin & see through! They are thinner than they look. In my pics (without flash), you can see the peach/salmon blanket that is under the panties/undies. Now, I have always worn Fruit of the Loom or Hanes, in bikini or briefs. I am a 55 yr old who has had 2 abdomen surgeries, so now I stick to briefs only! I will tell you... I put these on and they are SO COMFORTABLE! I got them a little bigger, just because I ALWAYS allow for shrinkage when drying. In the pics you can see seems. You DO NOT feel them at all! I HATE any kind of seems; tags; lace; things that make me itch anything that bothers me is a complete NO! Nothing that is on these are an issue! The band is doubled, along with the crotch! The rest is a single piece of material. The stitching(see pic) is so nice! It is made so well, IMO. I just wish it was made a bit thicker all around, lime the Fruit of the Looms were. I like a warm hiney! LOL. Combine the 2 and they would be fantastic! I hope they last!! I would probably get these again. I just really love the band. If you think you wouldn't, DONT! I am so very picky when it comes to EVERYTHING! Theyse are a MUST TRY! I would say they fit as expect too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Do not crawl up nor bind
reviews.reviewText: These undies do not crawl up your backside, don't show "lines" and are generally extremely comfortable. This is coming from someone who usually has worn hipster underwear that also didn't crawl up but I'm fed up with Hanes getting holes after a few months. These seem like they are made of sturdier, stretchier fabric that will last better. Meantime, they are very comfortable. Love the colors for under winter clothing.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fantastic - my favorites now!
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely love these panties. I haven’t had them for too long, but I’ve washed them at least 5 times. I choose them over all my others, every time.These feel good, come up high enough on the waist, are soft with no irritating seams, and give enough support that you feel good. Not too tight like compression or shape wear, just secure. They are a little stretchy but not too much.They aren’t cheeky, and I hope they stay that way after many washes. Sometimes panties give out. So far, so good.I buy mostly cotton underwear, not silky, lacy, or polyester fabrics. Sometimes other fabrics like bamboo or modal are ok, but cotton is best. And that’s what these are.So glad I tried them! Will be ordering more!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I’ve been searching for full brief underwear that fit. These have the perfect amount of cotton, stretch and coverage. I’ve already ordered 10 more pair. I ordered “name brand” briefs at the same time I ordered these. The H—-s brand quality was nearly as nice, well fitting and comfortable as these briefs. If in doubt- buy them!

Very comfortable! Soft and seamless yet thick. They feel luxurious. The wide band keeps them in place. I bought them for work and workouts so I'm not always hiking up my underpants. I was scared they were going to look like granny panties with the high waist but they don't, they look super cute. I will definitely be ordering more :)

reviews.reviewTitle: Quality material is very soft. Fits well.
reviews.reviewText: The five colours are nice, 3 basic (white , grey and black) and then the red and creamsicle ones are . The high waist fits well and doesn’t roll down with wear. I’ll definitely order again. 🙂
I like how comfortable they feel. I'm not sure how they will feel though when the weather gets warmer - since they are so high waisted and the fabric is pretty dense, they might be feel too hot...
Bought these for the first time and found them to be of good fabric, excellent fit and most comfortable for all day wear! Would highly recommend it!
